%N A395709 Expansion of g^5*(5*g-4)/(4-3*g)^4, where g = 1+x*g^4 is the g.f. of A002293.
%F A395709 a(n) = (n+1) * A386565(n+1).
%F A395709 G.f.: (Sum_{k>=0} (4*k+1)/(2*k+1) * binomial(4*k+2,k) * x^k) * (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(4*k,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395709 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k^2 = (1/3) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(4*k-1,k) * x^k ).
%F A395709 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(4*k+3+l,k) * binomial(4*n-4*k-l,n-k) for every real number l.
%F A395709 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 3^(n-k) * binomial(4*n+4,k).
%F A395709 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 4^(n-k) * binomial(3*n+k+3,k).
%o A395709 (PARI) a(n) = (n+1)*sum(k=0, n, 3^(n-k)*binomial(4*n+4, k));
